          <img src="/images/assets/sagittarius.png" alt="sagittarius">
          <p class="zod-name">Sagittarius</p>
          <p class="bday">Nov 22 - Dec 21</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div id="fourth-row">
        <a id="capricorn" class="zodiac-img" href="/zodiacs/622a6bb1091201cb08c47a03">
